{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>如下所示的由正整数数字构成的三角形:<p><p>7<p><p>3 8<p><p>8 1 0<p><p>2 7 4 4<p><p>4 5 2 6 5<p><p>从三角形的顶部到底部有很多条不同的路径。对于每条路径，把路径上面的数加起来可以得到一个和，和最大的路径称为最佳路径。你的任务就是求出最佳路径上的数字之和。<p><p>注意：路径上的每一步只能从一个数走到下一层上和它最近的下边(正下方)的数或者右边（右下方）的数。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"三角形最佳路径问题 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>最佳路径的长度数值。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第一行为三角形高度100≥h≥1，同时也是最底层边的数字的数目。<p><p>从第二行开始，每行为三角形相应行的数字，中间用空格分隔。<p>","examples":"<input>5\n7\n3 8\n8 1 0\n2 7 4 4\n4 5 2 6 5\n</input><output>30\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1288","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}